text: Kamilukuak Lake is a large lake in the Kivalliq Region of Nunavut in Canada. Part of the lake to the west lies in the Northwest Territories. The lake is 25 km south of Dubawnt Lake. ==See also== *List of lakes of Nunavut *List of lakes of Canada == References == Category:Lakes of Kivalliq Region
title: Kamilukuak Lake
